steps.name: I am on the Home Page "https://www.carsguide.com.au" of carsguide website
I click on "Used" link from Used Cars search page
I select car brand  as "Audi" from Any Make dropdown from Used Cars search page
I select car model of Used Cars search page
I select Location as "SA - All" from Any Location dropdown from Used Cars search page
I select Price as "$10,000" from Price dropdown of Used Cars search page
I click on Find_My_Next_Car button from Used Cars search page
I should see the list of Used cars  from Used Cars search page
The page title should be "Used Audi A4 Under 10000 for Sale SA - Second Hand Audi A4 Under $10k in SA | carsguide"
